# Note: we deliberately do NOT list nodejs / npm here. The build uses
# whatever Node is on PATH (in CI: actions/setup-node@v4; on a dev
# machine: whatever the maintainer has). dpkg-checkbuilddeps only sees
# apt-installed packages, so listing them here would force apt-nodejs
# on the build host even when a newer Node is already available.
