# Package rename: bitsby8 supersedes fdcsds. Conflicts+Replaces make apt
# remove the old package and take over its files; Provides keeps any local
# operator scripts that still reference `fdcsds` satisfiable.
Replaces: fdcsds
Conflicts: fdcsds
Provides: fdcsds
Description: BitsBy8 Serial Drive Server for Altair 8800
 A Serial Disk Server compatible with the FDC+ Enhanced Floppy Disk
 Controller for the Altair 8800 vintage computer.
 .
 This TypeScript/Node.js implementation provides:
  - Serial disk emulation for vintage Altair 8800 computers
  - Multi-drive support (up to 4 drives)
  - Web interface with real-time monitoring
  - VT102 terminal emulator for serial console
  - REST API for remote management
  - Configuration file support for easy deployment
 .
 The package includes systemd integration for automatic startup
 and sample disk images for testing.
